        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''I'm thankful I'm alive, but I feel guilty I'm alive. I'm trying to remember the guys who aren't here. Their wives and children. It's a hollow feeling. You try to laugh sometimes to keep your sanity, but you feel bad about laughing.''</p>
        <p>ROBERT MADDALONE, Firefighter, Squad 1 [B8]</p>
      </block>
